name: Angle of The Dangle
description:
Angle of the dangle is the first in a series of pieces by @Brave Temple
commemorating phrases known as Lou-isms. A Lou-ism is a saying/phrase used to convey a general idea typically using comedic timing in an applicable situation. The Lou-ism that inspired this piece is [Its all about the angle of the dangle]
This Lou-ism is used in a comedic fashion when preforming a task or activity that requires  finesse,precision,and skill to complete.
Lou may use this phrase while using a claw machine as he carefully positions the claw and successfully claims his prize.
Thanks for all the good times Lou, Love you buddy.
